{
  "texts": [
    "Hybrid fusion approaches attempted to balance these aspects by integrating modalities at intermediate layers, showing promise in certain applications [15], [16].",
    "Studies revealed that the choice of fusion technique significantly impacted the performance of AI systems, particularly in tasks requiring deep contextual understanding [3], [17], [18].",
    "Challenges were noted in the alignment of feature scales and modal contributions, which sometimes led to suboptimal results [1], [19], [20].",
    "The complexity of synthesizing multimodal data effectively to improve AI system interpretations has been revealed repeatedly [21].",
    "Despite advances, optimal fusion methods that can universally apply across different domains remain elusive."
  ]
}